      <div class="msgContentFrame">Hey everyone I had a couple questions on how you are setting up your Hot Bar.  I don't even know if thats what it is called but i'm gonna go with.  I am currently Level 12 Thaumaturge and I find it kinda frustrating that I have all of these spells and can only allocate so many.  I was wondering if people could give me a rundown of what they are using around this level for doing leve quests or just exp grinds.   <br /> <br />Also as a Thaumaturge should I be focusing more on magic accuracy for all the dots and debuffs?  This job is kinda out of my comfort zone considering on most MMO's i've played I usually just play a melee class.   <br /> <br />Well anyway any advice or theorys are greatly appreciated thanks in Advance! <br /> <br />Richard Scary - Lindblum Server</div>
