      <div class="msgContentFrame">How i have mine setup is this, just works for me <br /> <br />1 Spirit Dart <br />2 Poison <br />3 Dia <br />4 Sacrifice <br />5 Cure (from Conjurer) <br />6 Guard (didn't put it there, just goes there when i have a shield equiped &gt;.&gt;) <br />7 Punishing Barbs <br />8 Stoneskin (Conjurer) <br />9 Blood Rite <br />0 Exaltation <br /> <br />don't have anymore points yet to put more spells down yet.<div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div> <br /><img src="http://common.zam.com/xivsigs/1817536.png" alt="Signature Image" border="0" /> <br /></div></div>
